Rating: 4
This recipe is truly awesome.The ingredients blend so well together. I did add garlic powder and a splash of honey. It cuts the saltiness of the oyster sauce. The sauce gave the asparagus a wonderful taste. Lots of sauce on flank and go sparsely on the vegetable. Definitely a keeper. The cooking times are extremely accurate.

